vars <- c("cold_area", "u10m_IQR",  "bh_200", "imp_200")

mod <- lapply(vars, function(x) paste0("s(", x, ")") ) %>% paste(collapse = " + ") 

ms <- paste("gam(log(value) ~ ", mod, ", gamma=1.4, family=gaussian(link=log), data = df)")

mod <- eval(parse(text = ms))

summary(mod)
